                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150913-19-off96 t18150913-19-crimeloc99"></join>. I know nothing of the particulars of the robbery of my own knowledge. The prisoner was brought into my shop, and this piece of cotton, which Bengal, the officer, has produced, was taken out of his apron, and it is my property, it has my shop mark upon it; it is worth one pound seven shillings at prime cos.</p>
